                    "strokes": [],
                    "effects": [],
                    "characters": "In this file, you’ll be able to access some of the UI3 assets our design teams use internally to build Figma’s products. You'll find resources like color and typography variables, atomic components such as buttons and inputs, documentation, and larger templates for Figma Design, FigJam, and Slides.  \nWhile this file doesn't encompass every element from our internal library, our goal is to continue update it with more components and templates as our library evolves and as needed based on community feedback. Whether you’re a design systems designer, plugin/widget developer, or someone just interested in learning more about Figma, we hope you find some value in this file!",
